data.description: One of Stone Crest Estate's stunning new floor plans, known as the Burton, features three bedrooms, including a phenomenal master suite, and two bathrooms. With a stunning, upgraded kitchen that overlooks the living room and dining room, a spacious two-car garage and bedrooms with large closets, this home was designed with your family in mind. Positioned perfectly on large acreage lots, start living the life you love in Stone Crest Estate today!
